Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:57.65,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃える緋の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:01:00.15,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}There I'll find my place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:03.67,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Under the rader I'm reaching for the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:10.18,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鋼の牙を起て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:18.76,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}呻きと声を挙げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:25.74,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I'm gonna live out my life untamed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:17.62,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}たった―つのこの身焦がして
