Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:25.44,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}内燃机频频轰鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:27.81,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生命仍将延续
