Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:03.67,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}雷达之下寻找自己的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:10.18,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起钢刃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:18.76,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}纵情呻吟
